      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example has been maintained with technical rigor: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point in the E46 chassis\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The engine utilizes its individual throttle bodies to deliver immediate throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a factory variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains its factory geometry for a balanced weight distribution and communicative steering feel. It is a mechanically sorted enthusiast car that prioritizes performance and structural longevity over showroom aesthetics.",
