      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather seats are in great shape with only light softening on the driver-side bolster, and the dashboard is free from any sun damage or cracking. Every feature, from the heated seats to the infotainment system and sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly without any leaks or unusual noises. I have kept up with a rigorous maintenance schedule, including a recent oil change, coolant flush, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight, shifts crisply, and offers a quiet ride, making it a reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
